Description: Convert text with ANSI escape codes to HTML
 A PHP library that converts text containing ANSI escape sequences into HTML.
 It supports multiple color themes (Solarized, SolarizedXTerm, AnsiTheme)
 and provides an optional Twig extension bridge for template integration.
